{"tid":1511403,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"冷靜對待警員家屬","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:05:51.000Z","uid":229835,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0a342f1fc4d7fca9f99f21ae8f462419e7a61a","tid":1511403,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">冷</span></strong></span>靜<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>對待</strong></span></span>警員家屬<br />\n<br />\n大家從來都只見到夫妻鬥咀, 互罵一輩子<br />\n卻不會, 也不能一輩也不對話<br />\n冷漠是感情最大傷害, 連吵架的動力都冇<br />\n因為對方被你無視, 被你認為無價值<br />\n<br />\n從另一個角度, 大家明白童言無忌<br />\n但說者無心, 聽者有意, 為保護自己小朋友<br />\n與警方子女保持距離, 方為上策<br />\n<br />\n請於校園內, 冷靜對待警方家屬<br />\n沒對話, 沒眼神, 沒溝通"},{"pid":"4cfd35b889665350dea33b3ef5eace336747b276","tid":1511403,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"預左負評, 歡迎批評"},{"pid":"dcea9042fd2b681600efabc8c465fb65d3cd9fb5","tid":1511403,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5e3cb25d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=373ce7f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&